divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my friends where sitting outside talking when one of my friends looked in the sky and what is that cruising by us in the sky. at first we thought it was an comic,shooting star,burning satellite etc. so it left then 5 mins. later it came back again but this time it was more visible we can tell it was an unknown object,nothing that fly's thru the sky looks like what we saw but then it vanished. then it came back a third time as if it was doing circles around us this time u can see things poking from the side off it. i tried 2 call my brother an tell him what was going on but he say the phone was stat icing then it just cruised thru the sky and left.
